abstract: >-
  Concept paper proposing CIVITAS Public as a concrete first step towards a
  European digital civic infrastructure. CIVITAS Public is conceived as a
  non-commercial, open-source, multilingual platform for verified publication,
  structured debate, polling, trend observation, civic questions, and future
  participatory expansion — governed by transparent rules, independent oversight,
  and rule-of-law safeguards. Part of the ERDA Initiative.
